extends AbstractIdFetcher
implements com.semanticbits.security.contentfilter.IdFetcher

Will find the Reporting Periods a logged-in person has access to. This will work-off the Participant Index. Assumptions:- ============= The roles requiring subject Indexing are :- Site Scoped Roles: NONE Study Scoped Roles: UserGroupType.ae_reporter, UserGroupType.ae_expedited_report_reviewer, UserGroupType.ae_study_data_reviewer, UserGroupType.data_reader, UserGroupType.data_analyst The Participant Index is available at the time for the given login-Id

Author:
Srini Akkala, Biju Joseph
